      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1779751096887,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Functional Requirements\n- view a list of problems\n- view a given problem and code a solution\n- submit a solution and get feedback\n- support competitions w/ live leaderboard\n\nNon-functional Requirements\n- availability >> consistency\n- security and isolation when running users code\n- scale to support competitions with 100k users\n- freshness -> near-realtime\n\nScale\n- 100M DAU\n- 3K problems\n- 100k peak for competitions\n\n\n\n\n\n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Functional Requirements\n- view a list of problems\n- view a given problem and code a solution\n- submit a solution and get feedback\n- support competitions w/ live leaderboard\n\nNon-functional Requirements\n- availability >> consistency\n- security and isolation when running users code\n- scale to support competitions with 100k users\n- freshness -> near-realtime\n\nScale\n- 100M DAU\n- 3K problems\n- 100k peak for competitions\n\n\n\n\n\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "SkxSETBtQnbPqG0DeEoxj",
      "type": "text",
